<sect1 id="dir_c723e3cec65e0ebbf524b85c829eaed3_1autotoc_md311">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::spawn::components</title><para>Components for spawn-related entity tracking.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_c723e3cec65e0ebbf524b85c829eaed3_1autotoc_md312">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides components that track spawn-related metadata on GameObjects. These components enable the spawn/despawn pipeline to route entities to the correct pools and managers.</para>
</sect1>
